{"4071460": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Tentacle Locker 2", "steam_appid": 4071460, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/b178b73c08da8472f35254d9ec429653.poster.avif?t=1771537292\" width=780 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/b178b73c08da8472f35254d9ec429653.webm?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/b178b73c08da8472f35254d9ec429653.mp4?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一隻鬼鬼祟祟的觸手怪，在繁忙的校園走廊中四處出沒。你可以躲進儲物櫃中等待時機，在恰到好處的瞬間跳出來抓住路過的角色並獲得分數。抓到的角色越多，賺到的錢也就越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在校園的每個角落製造輕鬆又歡樂的混亂吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/53ccaa75f38eab4b863e93c528eb6dd5.poster.avif?t=1771537292\" width=780 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/53ccaa75f38eab4b863e93c528eb6dd5.webm?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/53ccaa75f38eab4b863e93c528eb6dd5.mp4?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲採用簡單的橫向捲軸玩法，操作直觀，新手也能輕鬆上手。你需要在不同的儲物櫃之間移動，仔細把握時機，選擇最合適的瞬間出手。如果錯過了時機，所有角色都會立刻逃走。你能成功抓住多少人呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你辛苦賺來的金幣，解鎖各種有趣的外觀升級內容。包括不同主題的走廊裝飾，以及為學生添加的各種俏皮小配件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲包含多種角色設計，並且會隨著你解鎖更多外觀配件而變得更加豐富多樣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在不同的走廊場景之間切換，體驗更加多樣化的遊戲內容。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/b178b73c08da8472f35254d9ec429653.poster.avif?t=1771537292\" width=780 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/b178b73c08da8472f35254d9ec429653.webm?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/b178b73c08da8472f35254d9ec429653.mp4?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一隻鬼鬼祟祟的觸手怪，在繁忙的校園走廊中四處出沒。你可以躲進儲物櫃中等待時機，在恰到好處的瞬間跳出來抓住路過的角色並獲得分數。抓到的角色越多，賺到的錢也就越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在校園的每個角落製造輕鬆又歡樂的混亂吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/53ccaa75f38eab4b863e93c528eb6dd5.poster.avif?t=1771537292\" width=780 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/53ccaa75f38eab4b863e93c528eb6dd5.webm?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/extras/53ccaa75f38eab4b863e93c528eb6dd5.mp4?t=1771537292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲採用簡單的橫向捲軸玩法，操作直觀，新手也能輕鬆上手。你需要在不同的儲物櫃之間移動，仔細把握時機，選擇最合適的瞬間出手。如果錯過了時機，所有角色都會立刻逃走。你能成功抓住多少人呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你辛苦賺來的金幣，解鎖各種有趣的外觀升級內容。包括不同主題的走廊裝飾，以及為學生添加的各種俏皮小配件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲包含多種角色設計，並且會隨著你解鎖更多外觀配件而變得更加豐富多樣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在不同的走廊場景之間切換，體驗更加多樣化的遊戲內容。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "在這款輕鬆有趣的橫版遊戲中，你將扮演一隻調皮搗蛋的觸手怪。你可以藏在儲物櫃裡伺機而動，找準時機跳出來抓住毫無防備的學生來賺取金幣。用賺到的錢解鎖各種搞怪的外觀裝飾，在地圖裡盡情製造歡樂又混亂的場面吧！", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文, 韓文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/ee78bb59adc99344b517244e28b0884de28ee045/header.jpg?t=1771537292", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/b1c4a73c9690551bfad2a89258a54a008b5c499e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1771537292", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071460/b1c4a73c9690551bfad2a89258a54a008b5c499e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1771537292", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "legal_notice": "2026 Saikey Studios", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}